{"tid":1254830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［入黎討論啦］事已至此 抗爭路應該點行落去？","createTime":"2019-06-24T09:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T12:22:50.000Z","uid":203499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c980e417bbd1441c0b208db93477e8633c636827","tid":1254830,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"經過今日一事<br />\n成個熱門都係互屌post<br />\n<br />\n勇武又好 和理非又好<br />\n唔好再嘈喇好嘛<br />\n<br />\n無論支唔支持 有冇出黎<br />\n成功係一齊成功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗都係一齊失敗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日圍税局嘅效果係不爭嘅事實<br />\n抗爭仲未完<br />\n政府仲未回應<br />\n義士仲未被釋放<br />\n<br />\n與其繼續喺度互屌<br />\n不如求同存異 和而不同<br />\nfocus番喺而家應該做嘅事度？<br />\n<br />\n當務之急會唔會係做好文宣<br />\n大肆宣傳626？<br />\n<br />\n有幾張圖講解26至27嘅計劃<br />\nshare出黎大家參考下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xxoZFZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xxoZFZ.png&h=395164b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5irXsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5irXsF.png&h=e9e6e192&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVYSS03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVYSS03.png&h=0c960c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PoUbo7L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPoUbo7L.png&h=9e455f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街站又好 長輩圖又好 ig乜都好<br />\n各位手足一齊盡最大努力向同一目標進發好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n至於626之後可以點做<br />\n成功之後點 失敗之後點<br />\n都係要靠大家一齊去思考去計劃<br />\n<br />\n我唔想消費犧牲嘅烈士<br />\n但既然大家識屌人係咪遺忘左佢<br />\n不妨都以此提醒下自己 <br />\n唔好比自己一刻嘅灰心同嬲怒打沉<br />\n繼續合作 we connect <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWMJfdT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWMJfdT.png&h=1522a312&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a18ac6dd9fa89c747e0e898dab7ba05a42ccb07","tid":1254830,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:39:32.000Z","m